127
00:09:16,805 --> 00:09:18,223
I haven't been to school, Mum.

128
00:09:18,849 --> 00:09:19,850
It's the morning.

129
00:09:20,893 --> 00:09:21,894
Is it?

130
00:09:22,060 --> 00:09:23,061
JAMIE: Er, yeah,

131
00:09:23,812 --> 00:09:25,188
