154
00:10:08,190 --> 00:10:09,983
Are you trying to kill
our fucking baby, you cunt?

155
00:10:10,067 --> 00:10:11,443
Spike, will you go back
downstairs, please?

156
00:10:11,526 --> 00:10:12,861
You crazy fucking
sick baby-murderer.

157
00:10:13,028 --> 00:10:14,154
No, Dad, you go down.

158
00:10:14,238 --> 00:10:15,447
-If me dad was still here...
-JAMIE: No, I'm telling you.

159
00:10:15,530 --> 00:10:16,531
