160
00:10:16,615 --> 00:10:17,616
JAMIE: It'll be better if...
All right!

161
00:10:17,699 --> 00:10:18,700
-Cunt!
-All right. Isla,

162
00:10:18,784 --> 00:10:19,785
-it's all right.
-Cunt!

163
00:10:19,868 --> 00:10:22,079
-All right. He'll be fine.
-Cunt! [WHIMPERING]

164
00:10:22,829 --> 00:10:24,248
-SPIKE: Mum...
-No.

165
00:10:25,040 --> 00:10:26,583
